  "local_port": 52044,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "How do I reset my WeChat password?",
  "response": "To reset your WeChat password, follow these steps:\n\n### **Via the WeChat App:**\n1. **Open WeChat**: Launch the WeChat app on your device.\n2. **Go to Login Screen**: If you\u2019re not already on the login screen, log out of your account.\n3. **Select \"Forgot Password\"**: Tap on \"More Options\" or \"Forgot Password\" at the bottom of the login screen.\n4. **Choose Verification Method**:\n   - **SMS Verification**: Enter the phone number associated with your WeChat account and follow the instructions to receive a verification code via SMS. Enter the code to proceed.\n   - **Email Verification**: If you\u2019ve linked an email to your account, you can choose to verify via email instead.\n5. **Reset Password**: After verification, you\u2019ll be prompted to create and confirm a new password.\n6. **Log In**: Once your password is reset, log back into WeChat with your new credentials.\n\n### **Via WeChat Website (if you can\u2019t access the app):**\n1. **Visit the WeChat Help Center**: Go to [WeChat Help Center](https://help.wechat.com/).\n2. **Select \"Forgot Password\"**: Choose the \"Forgot Password\" option.\n3. **Enter Your Information**: Provide the phone number or email associated with your WeChat account.\n4. **Follow Verification Steps**: Verify your identity through SMS or email, as described above.\n5. **Reset Password**: Create and confirm your new password.\n6. **Log In**: Use your new password to log into WeChat.\n\n### **If You\u2019re Locked Out and Can\u2019t Verify:**\nIf you cannot access the phone number or email linked to your account:\n1. **Contact WeChat Support**: Use the WeChat Help Center to submit a request for assistance.\n2. **Provide Account Details**: You may need to provide additional information (e.g., account creation date, previous passwords, transaction history) to prove ownership of the account.\n3. **Wait for Response**: WeChat support will assist in recovering your account.\n\n### **Tips:**\n- Make sure you have access to the phone number or email linked to your account before starting the process.\n- If you\u2019re using a phone number, ensure it can receive SMS or has roaming enabled if you\u2019re abroad.\n- Always use a secure, unique password for your account.\n\nIf you encounter issues, visit the [WeChat Help Center](https://help.wechat.com/) for further assistance.",
